# InputSystem

## Purpose
Aggregates all raw input event components into a single InputStateSingletonComponent each frame.
Maintains per-key held-frame counters (incremented every frame a key stays pressed), clears
one-frame data (released keys, typed characters), and translates platform key codes to engine
constants via PlatformInput before writing to the singleton.

## Input Components
| Component | Access |
|---|---|
| KeyPressedEventComponent | read |
| KeyReleasedEventComponent | read |
| KeyTypedEventComponent | read |
| MouseMovedEventComponent | read |
| MouseButtonPressedEventComponent | read |
| MouseButtonReleasedEventComponent | read |
| MouseScrolledEventComponent | read |
| InputStateSingletonComponent | write |

## Output Components
| Component | Access | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| InputStateSingletonComponent | write / add (deferred) | Created on first frame; updated every frame with aggregated key, mouse, and scroll state |
